  id: tutorial_gamestart
  title: Dev Controls
  body: 'Arrow keys = Move farmer


    Digit key keybinds:

    1: Call Plant()       
    2: Call Harvest()


    Resource Managing:

    "[": Add resources      "]":
    Remove resources

    7: Money        8: Fruits        9: Vegetables        9:
    Berries

    Hold down a bracket key, then press one of the digit keys to add/remove
    the corresponding resource. Add 10 money to see the tutorial for a shop.'
  trigger: 0
  thresholdResource: 0
  thresholdAmount: 0
